rows.label: tlk006301_09_msg0001
rows.name:
Perhaps due to our proximity to the World Tree,
Luxuria has not yet
suffered significant damage.

rows.label: tlk006301_09_msg0002
rows.name:
However, I saw various Divine Beasts in the distance
sinking into the Cloud Sea...

rows.label: tlk006301_09_msg0003
rows.name: ...This must be the end of Alst.

rows.label: tlk006301_09_msg0004
rows.name:
When I think that Luxuria's decision 500 years ago
may have led to this current situation,
my heart aches.
